Got it. âœ… Since you're currently storing cart data only in Session, it gets cleared on logout. To fix this without changing too much, weâ€™ll store cart items in the database linked to the logged-in customer â€” instead of just session.

Letâ€™s follow these minimal steps based on your current setup:


